page.title: 03 LIFE STYLES
page.content: JUSTINS DAY. GOT UP AT 6:00am TO DO MY NEWSPAPER ROUND.FOR BREAKFAST I EITHER HAVE CORNFLAKES,SUGAR PUFFS,WEETABIX OR TOAST TO EAT.I THEN PUT MY SCHOOL UNIFORM OF SHIRT,JUMPER,BLACK TROUSERS, TIE AND BLAZER ON.I CLEAN MY TEETH WITH TOOTHPASTE AND BRUSH AND THEN GO DOWN- STAIRS AND PACK MY LUNCH .I WATCH BREAKFAST TELEVISION BEFORE CYCLING TO SCHOOL ON MY 5 SPEED RACER.AT SCHOOL I PLAY "BUM"WHICH IS A BALL GAME PLAYED LIKE TABLE TENNIS BUT WITH YOUR HANDS THEN I GO TO FORM PERIOD FOR REGISTER. I STUDY HISTORY,FRENCH,ENGLISH,MATHS, SCIENCE,MUSIC,GAMES,GEOGRAPHY,ART AND CRAFT SUBJECTS.AFTER SCHOOL I EITHER WATCH TELEVISION,GO SWIMMING,MEET MY FRIENDS AT THE YOUTH CLUB OR PLAY ON MY COMPUTER.I GO TO BED AT 9:30pm AFTER COMPLETING MY HOMEWORK.
